{{vgname|赛车计划|en=Project CARS}}是一款由[[Slightly_Mad_Studios|Slightly Mad Studios]]开发并由[[万代南梦宫游戏|万代南梦宫游戏]]发行在[[PlayStation_4|PlayStation 4]]、[[Xbox_One|Xbox One]]、[[Windows|Windows]]和[[Linux|Linux]]等平台上的[[竞速游戏|竞速模拟]]游戏。游戏最早计划作为[[PlayStation_3|PlayStation 3]]和[[Xbox_360|Xbox 360]]两个平台的游戏开发，但之后宣布取消这两个平台的开发计划并将平台移至[[PlayStation_4|PlayStation 4]]和[[Xbox_One|Xbox One]]，并增加[[Wii_U|Wii U]]、[[Windows|Windows]]和[[Linux|Linux]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://kotaku.com/gorgeous-racing-game-does-the-smart-thing-abandons-cur-1459865337|title=Gorgeous Racing Game Does The Smart Thing, Abandons Current-Gen|publisher=[[Kotaku|Kotaku]]|access-date=2015-01-20|archive-date=2015-05-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150509215703/http://kotaku.com/gorgeous-racing-game-does-the-smart-thing-abandons-cur-1459865337|dead-url=no}}</ref>随后，Wii U版也遭到取消。<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.nintendolife.com/news/2015/07/exclusive_project_cars_simply_too_much_for_wii_u_developer_now_waiting_on_new_nintendo_hardware | title=Exclusive: Project CARS "Simply Too Much For Wii U", Developer Now Waiting On New Nintendo Hardware | work=Nintendo Life | first=Damien | last=McFerran | date=July 21, 2015 | accessdate=July 21, 2015 | archive-date=2015-07-23 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150723001104/http://www.nintendolife.com/news/2015/07/exclusive_project_cars_simply_too_much_for_wii_u_developer_now_waiting_on_new_nintendo_hardware | dead-url=no }}</ref>游戏还会支持[[Oculus_Rift|Oculus Rift]]和索尼的[[PlayStation_VR|PlayStation VR]][[虚拟现实|虚拟现实]]显示设备。<ref name="Oculus Rift Support Announcement">{{cite web |title=Oculus Rift virtual reality headset announcement |url=http://forum.wmdportal.com/showthread.php?8930-This-Week-In-Project-CARS-2012-34 |access-date=2015-01-20 |archive-date=2015-07-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150722081732/http://forum.wmdportal.com/showthread.php?8930-This-Week-In-Project-CARS-2012-34 |dead-url=no }}</ref> 

《赛车计划》在经过多次延期后于2015年5月7日起在全球陆续发售，并在发售后获得了不错的评价。

游戏续作《[[賽車計劃2|賽車計劃2]]》於2017年9月22日與全球同步正式發售。

